lih.kg/1827641\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/1827641</a><span style=\"color: red;\">宣傳ddos連登的大陸百度貼吧(太多不盡錄)</span><br />\n<code>3 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/iFatvbX\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/iFatvbX</a><span style=\"color: red;\">主張連登行實名制</span><br />\n<code>4 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/NJvjmV\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/NJvjmV</a><span style=\"color: red;\">謊稱自己要參選 但最後冇咗件事</span><br />\n<code>5 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/1208009\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/1208009</a><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍冷血言論</span><br />\n<code>6 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/1615186\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/1615186</a><span style=\"color: red;\">義士中槍當日開咩白滑唔知乜春嘅垃圾帖</span><br />\n<code>7 .</code><a href=\"http://lih.kg/1125330\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/1125330</a><span style=\"color: red;\">宣傳吹奏大陸cosplayer(太多不盡錄)</span><br />\n<code>8 .</code><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1885800\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1885800</a><span style=\"color: red;\">轉載來自極端吹奏大陸嘅微博--多啦聯盟</span><br />\n<code>9 .</code><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1890495\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1890495</a><span style=\"color: red;\">宣傳支那人</span><br />\n<code>10 .</code><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1889915\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1889915</a><span style=\"color: red;\">宣傳奶共臭閪電影花木蘭</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">「歷史回顧，無忘初心」</div><pre><code data-type=\"\">2019年7月21日\n毋忘721元朗恐襲</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1QaXHUZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1QaXHUZ.jpg&h=b7bf4f8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">我要真雙普選</code></pre><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/56Kq4TS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F56Kq4TS.jpg&h=3605f423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">「文宣」</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q3rWYzB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ3rWYzB.jpg&h=87c9e947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XThZWkz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXThZWkz.png&h=f963a4cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1291657\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1291657</a>"},{"pid":"df79fcf1a90c5d448087c4c5d752163027f98dc8","tid":2063334,"uid":128089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f21786dce5cca59cf4249f2e78b76b209a98ceb7","tid":2063334,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T02:52:54.000Z","msg":"5毛 遠阪凜#3020 手持至少6個連登帳號,請admin跟進<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1291657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1291657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n熱烈恭賀牙井當選區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1751830\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1751830</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔好回覆呢個post，唔好幫佢賺錢！<br />\n會員#3020遠阪凜係連登知名過街老鼠及5毛！<br />\n牽涉多單竊取會員資料，宣傳特定網頁！<br />\n多次洗版式帶風向，包括慌稱自己是一名抗爭者，扮演手足！<br />\n混淆視聽話自己要參選區議會，以及不斷活躍於政治帖意圖帶風向！<br />\n甚至協助ddos連登等行為，已經係證據確鑿！<br />\n鬼知佢背後有咩動機，總之block咗佢就最一了百了！<br />\n請大家留意！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T05:08:23.000Z","msg":"你哋宜家屌鳩台主嗰啲嘢......<br />\n<br />\n我早你哋七年前已經屌緊啦！<br />\n<br />\n成班語無倫次，搞利益集團，講說話冇文化冇內涵，拍埋啲嘢冇公共性。<br />\n<br />\n我睇住動物台由型轉柒，咁多年講咗不下十次。<br />\n<br />\n不過台主柒還柒呀，你宜家話人係政府喉舌，又有冇證據呀？<br />\n<br />\n當年高登連登仲有人撐楊岳橋，但台主係公開支持梁天琦架喎！<br />\n<br />\n你有權覺得檢舉bam圖係不道德，但係你哋憑咩話人暗共呀？<br />\n<br />\n你哋係咪熱狗嚟㗎？<br />\n<br />\n有咩證據可以證明到佢哋係政府嘅契弟呀？<br />\n<br />\n隔離仲有個KOL叫你做兄弟，但係唔理你生死。<br />\n<br />\n被你問多兩句就發脾氣屌鳩你，到宜家都冇回應又唔道歉。<br />\n<br />\n佢啲言行有曬記錄同證據㗎喎！<br />\n<br />\n結果隔一排出返嚟試水溫做直播，大家又可以繼續睇得好開心，留言話達朝萬歲，<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，有個毒撚柒頭。<br />\n<br />\n我屌咗佢地啲柒嘢好多年，但係你地之前又唔敢join我一齊屌。<br />\n<br />\n結果宜家冇證據，你哋又突然話人係政府喉舌，係暗共。<br />\n<br />\n所以大家就要一齊對抗暗共，抵制台主<br />\n<br />\n你哋條標準點訂架？<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想叫大家停手，唔好殺人。<br />\n<br />\n我只係想指出你地公私不分，出師無名。<br />\n<br />\n如果你哋要加入我，一齊對抗快餐文化，對抗大台文化。<br />\n<br />\n我就無任歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n但如果你要夾硬作藉口，屈鳩任何人係暗共。<br />\n<br />\n我就絕不能苟同，此風不可長！<br />\n<br />\n就算你話達哥係暗共，我都係一樣咁話。<br />\n<br />\n係咪你唔妥佢，就可以屈佢係鬼？<br />\n<br />\n咁仲係唔係不分化不割蓆？<br />\n<br />\n話人係鬼，好大指控喎，究竟宜家係咪有證據呀？"},{"pid":"6549348866d7bb70b069be57e0f9b4ef3514ea28","tid":2063334,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:23:28.000Z","msg":"睇落似係h漫嘅節奏<br />\n<br />\n性轉後性上癮<br />\n跟住去做雞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"184051d9383a62e68015d4078fab22ffb3c37883","tid":2063334,"uid":132935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6549348866d7bb70b069be57e0f9b4ef3514ea28","tid":2063334,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:23:28.000Z","msg":"睇落似係h漫嘅節奏<br />\n<br />\n性轉後性上癮<br />\n跟住去做雞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:37:51.000Z","msg":"咪新堂個本，超耐歷史"},{"pid":"d8b2c7c58ca178b9398fb3641a6055506cfedc0b","tid":2063334,"uid":130563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:42:27.000Z","msg":"5毛 遠阪凜#3020 手持至少6個連登帳號,請admin跟進<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1291657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1291657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n熱烈恭賀牙井當選區議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1751830\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.